{
  "text": "Isothermal experiments carried out on the DSC exhibited time-dependent exothermic events due to crystallization. These events were analyzed and kinetic parameters were determined by computing a running integral across the event by a method similar to that described by Zhou et al. [CITATION_1] The crystal fraction, , was then obtained by normalizing the integral. Models were then evaluated based on best fit to the data to obtain kinetic information.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "25523464"
  },
